## 五、配对与连接流程

### 5.1 设备发现 (Inquiry)

```
Master → Inquiry Scan (手机搜索)
Slave → Inquiry Response (音箱响应)

Inquiry: 发送ID Packet (72个跳频)
Inquiry Scan: 监听Inquiry
Inquiry Response: 返回BD_ADDR + Clock + Class of Device
```

### 5.2 配对 (Pairing)

```
1. 传统配对 (BT 2.0-):
   - PIN码输入 (0000, 1234, 或自定义)
   - 链路密钥 (Link Key) 生成
   - 加密启用

2. 安全简单配对 (SSP, BT 2.1+):
   - Just Works (无用户交互)
   - Numeric Comparison (数字比较)
   - Passkey Entry (密码输入)
   - Out of Band (NFC)
```

### 5.3 连接 (Connection)

```
1. Page (寻呼):
   Master → Page (发送ID Packet)
   Slave → Page Response (响应)

2. Page Scan (寻呼扫描):
   Slave → Page Scan (监听Page)

3. 连接建立:
   Master → FHS Packet (包含BD_ADDR, Clock, etc.)
   Slave → 响应
   → 进入Connection State
```

